presentationNassim: I'm an actuary. But soccer is what defines me the most. I love skilled players, who can dribble, take risks and create new skills. I noticed that playing in the street was the best place to learn and improve. In 2013, I was recruited to play in an American university and I met there my teammate Jérémie. We shared the same point of view and decided we had to create something to help young player train the skills they want and show their talent. My goal is to make BestFootball become a platform of reference when it comes to training and football educative approach.
skillsNassim: Skills: vision, organisation and acceleration of the game
presentationJeremie: Althoug I come from a business school background, my true passion is Football. I had a chance to play all around the world, and especially in Lorient club and in USA where I met Nassim. I also worked with a company, helping young players to be recruited in USA. I may not be a top forward, but I have only one obsession: scoring. And I hope to score something big with BestFootball, making it a must-have application in the world.
presentationHamdi: I've been working for six years now as a web developer. As my partners, playing soccer has always been part of my life and I even dreamt to become professional at my younger age. To be happy, that's simple: give me a ball or lines to code. I joined this amazing team in 2018, and it's a pure pleasure for me to build something that will encourage and help many young to become stronger.
